                                <div class="q"><div style="padding:1rem 0;">"We Hungarians of Shanghai" is a history of the Hungarian community in old Shanghai. The book details the accomplishments of 60 Hungarian men and women.</div></div>
                                <div style="clear:both;"></div>
                            </div>
